more\naccessible proof of the result by P\\u{a}tra\\c{s}cu and Thorup, where the\nrelevant parts generalise nicely to the analysis of $d$ choices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Apr 2018 17:23:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-26"}
