io naturally explains the lack of the\nX-ray emission related to the ejecta and blastwave. The SNR-MC interaction also\nfavours a hadronic contribution to the {\\gamma}-ray emission from the CTB 87\nregion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Apr 2018 10:28:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 May 2018 13:32:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-13"}
