isc around them. The overall\nproperties of BCBs supports a picture of galaxy assembly in which younger discs\nare being accreted around massive pre-existing spheroids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Apr 2018 14:08:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-03"}
